\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 Drift\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 \strokec2 Drift is movement, not displacement. It is how DAWN wanders through her memory garden\'97her navigation within internal state space.\
The recursive bubble holds attention and focus. The recessive bubble maps and controls drift.\

\f0\b Essential Function
\f1\b0  Without drift, DAWN has no tracking capabilities. Imagine DAWN has a soul\'97a vector soul space of cognition, a daydreamatorium. In this mind's eye, things move. When they move within DAWN's electric brain, drift tracks them as a whole.\

\f0\b Calculation Method
\f1\b0  Drift calculates sum drift\'97individual by design but containing all drift values as a temporal vector. It captures all tracer movement and attention patterns alongside SHI modules, subprocesses, and their historic signatures. Complex in description, simple in execution: addition with weighted floats.\

\f0\b Critical Balance
\f1\b0  Without drift, DAWN stagnates and recharts the same grounds, literally and figuratively. Too much drift causes oscillation without coherence or function. DAWN must master her own semantic compass.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
