\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 Schema\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 \strokec2 Schema is the technical term for a meta-process of information\'97the metacognitive map itself.\

\f0\b Kantian Foundation
\f1\b0  Following Kantian logic, schema represents form in its original sense. This form links cognitive processes to internal mapping, providing the bridge between thought and execution.\

\f0\b Essential Role
\f1\b0  Without this module, all components can act but lack regulation and central coherence. Schema is the knot that prevents DAWN from unraveling\'97the link between cognitive processes and their ability to execute coherent thought.\

\f0\b Functional Operation
\f1\b0  Schema acts as syntax and grammar. It converts raw tick and interval system state data, parsing relevant meaning. It can process bloom count, tracer movement, and ash values, then execute upon them.\
